msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "Gravis PC Gamepad"
msgstr "Gravis PC Gamepad"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "The Gravis gamepad is a controller produced by Advanced Gravis Computer Technology in 1991. It was the first gamepad for the IBM PC in a market dominated by joysticks."
msgstr "Gravis gamepad je ovladač vyráběný společností Advanced Gravis Computer Technology od roku 1991. Byl to první gamepad pro IBM PC na trhu, kterému dominovaly joysticky."

